📌 Project Overview

The Beauty Blog Website is a modern and responsive blog designed to share beauty tips, skincare routines, and natural face mask recipes.

This project demonstrates:

Modern HTML5 semantic structure
Responsive CSS layout
Interactive JavaScript features
Scroll animations using AOS library
Dark Mode Toggle
Multi-page blog architecture

The website is designed to look like a professional beauty blog platform.

✨ Features
🌿 Organic Skincare Blog
💄 Lip Care Tips Article
🧴 Natural Face Mask Guide
🌙 Dark Mode Toggle
🎨 Responsive Mobile Design
🖼 Image Gallery with Hover Animation
🔗 Related Posts Section
✨ Scroll Animations (AOS)
🛠 Tech Stack
🎨 Frontend
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript (ES6)
🎨 Libraries
Font Awesome Icons
AOS Animation Library
