⚙️ Installation Guide
1️⃣ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/beauty-blog.git
cd beauty-blog
2️⃣ Open Project

Simply open the project folder and run:

index.html

or use Live Server in VS Code.

🚀 Deployment

You can deploy this project on:

Netlify
Vercel
GitHub Pages

Steps:

Push project to GitHub
Connect GitHub repo to Netlify / Vercel
Deploy website
